headline: Rimini Street and American Digital Partner to Deliver Alternative SAP, Oracle and VMware Support, Savings and Innovation on HPE Infrastructure
summary: LAS VEGAS, August 22, 2025--Rimini Street, Inc. (Nasdaq: RMNI), a global provider of end-to-end enterprise software support, management and innovation solutions, and the leading third-party support provider for Oracle, SAP and VMware software, today announced its strategic partnership with American Digital, a leading IT solutions provider specializing in custom data center solutions based on HPE infrastructure.
